#: app/templates/admin/index.html:9
msgid "Admin Panel"
msgstr "Panel Admin"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:11
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Grylli Admin Panel. Use the tools below to manage users, "
"configuration, and infrastructure-related settings."
msgstr ""
"Sugeng rawuh ing Panel Admin Grylli. Gunakake pranala ing ngisor iki kanggo "
"ngatur sistem."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:15
msgid "Manage Users"
msgstr "Ngatur Pangguna"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:16
msgid ""
"Create, edit, enable/disable, or delete user accounts. Control MFA, roles, "
"and recovery access."
msgstr "Nggawe, ngowahi, ngaktifake / mateni, utawa mbusak akun pangguna."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:19
#: app/templates/admin/system_settings.html:9
#: app/templates/partials/admin_nav.html:45
msgid "System Settings"
msgstr "Setelan Sistem"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:20
msgid "View environment configuration, default language, and public base URL."
msgstr "Deleng konfigurasi lingkungan, basa default, lan URL basis umum."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:23 app/templates/partials/admin_nav.html:35
msgid "Backups"
msgstr "Cadangan"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:24
msgid "Trigger or delete encrypted database backups."
msgstr "Dhukungan Database"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:28
msgid ""
"View and test the global SMTP configuration used for system-level emails."
msgstr ""
"Ndeleng lan nyoba konfigurasi SMTP global sing digunakake kanggo email "
"tingkat sistem."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:31
msgid "View Admin Guide / README"
msgstr "Deloken Pandhuan Admin / README ing GitHub"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:32
msgid ""
"Detailed setup, upgrade, and deployment instructions are available in the "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"Pandhuan rinci setelan, upgrade, lan deployment kasedhiya ing repositori."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:35
msgid "Manual Version Check"
msgstr "Mriksa Versi Manual"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:36
msgid ""
"Run this command from the host to manually check for new Grylli releases:"
msgstr ""
"Jalankan printah iki saka host kanggo mriksa manual rilis Grylli anyar:"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Tips Admin"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Aja tau mbukak ing produksi kanthi DEBUG diaktifake. Mode Debug mbuka "
"rincian internal lan jejak tumpukan."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Tansah nyebarke Grylli ing mburi proxy mbalikke (contone, Caddy, Nginx, "
"utawa Traefik) lan ladeni liwat HTTPS. Data pangguna sensitif kudu "
"dienkripsi nalika transit."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr "Pasthekna folder data (database) wis dicadhang ing host sampeyan"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Folder unggahan dibagi. Kanggo misahake lampiran saben pangguna, konfigurasi"
" direktori tingkat host lan kontrol akses."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Kanggo mulihake dhukungan: mandhegake kontainer, ganteni data/grylli.db "
"kanthi siji saka folder cadangan, lan miwiti maneh kontainer."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Admins ora bisa ngilangi peran admin dhewe kanggo nyegah terkunci kanthi ora"
" sengaja."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Wates tingkat lan terkunci akun otomatis ditetepake kanggo nglindhungi "
"marang upaya login brute-force."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr "Sandi, kredensial SMTP, lan API token di-enkripsi nganggo Fernet."

#: app/templates/admin/list_backups.html:11
msgid "Database Backups"
msgstr "Dhukungan Database"

#: app/templates/admin/list_backups.html:13
msgid ""
"Manage encrypted backups of your Grylli database. Only admins can create or "
"delete backups."
msgstr ""
"Ngatur serep sing dienkripsi saka basis data Grylli sampeyan. Mung admin "
"sing bisa nggawe utawa mbusak serep."

